title: Chinese Folk Designs (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Chinese Folk Designs
Dover Publications | 1971 | ISBN: 0486226336 | English | 324 pages | PDF | 38.8 MB


300 authentic, solid-silhouette designs printed in colors: phoenix, chrysanthemum, lotus, plum blossom, butterfly, fish, boat, etc. Provides rare source of ideas and direct reproduction wherever Oriental flavor is needed. One of the most aesthetically pleasing books to cross our desk in a long time!
